I’ve got the key test issue now: `profitToken()` starts as zero, so the harness ignores the DAI delta. I’m also calculating a valid current DAI permit so the replayed fills can actually execute on this fork.
exec
/bin/bash -lc 'PRIV=0xac0974bec39a17e36ba4a6b4d238ff944bacb478cbed5efcae784d7bf4f2ff80
DAI=0x6B175474E89094C44Da98b954EedeAC495271d0F
